# FounderLens – AI-Powered Business Analysis Platform

## Overview

FounderLens is an AI-powered business analysis platform designed to help founders, entrepreneurs, students, and business enthusiasts evaluate a business through strategic insights and data-driven recommendations.

The platform generates SWOT analyses, marketing audits, sales assessments, automation opportunities, business health scores, and growth roadmaps from simple business inputs.

This project was built as a portfolio project to demonstrate business analysis, product thinking, dashboard design, and AI-powered insight generation.

---

## Problem Statement

Many small businesses and startups struggle to identify operational inefficiencies, marketing gaps, and growth opportunities.

FounderLens simplifies this process by providing a structured business analysis framework that helps users understand their strengths, weaknesses, opportunities, threats, and next growth steps.

